Subject: EPP blocking web access to websites via Virtual Machines
Description:
Hello team,
It looks like EPP has started again to block access for mobile iOS virtual machines to any website. We have recently updated to MacOS Sonoma 14.5. Not sure if this is connected to the issue or not, but we've experienced this before and it was fixed in previous versions of EPP. Thank you
Solution_Comment__c: Issue was fixed with the previous EPP agent
Account_Name__c: The Stars Group Interactive Services / Flutter International
